# Obsidian Plugin Config

Vault is at `/Users/yourname/Documents/Obsidian`.

Run `/obsidian:setup` to generate this file interactively, or copy and edit manually.

## Project Taxonomy

| Domain | Vault path | Notes |
|--------|-----------|-------|
| Development | Projects/Development/ | Code, tools, debugging |
| Work | Projects/Work/ | Client/employer work, meetings |
| Personal | Projects/Personal/ | Personal notes, goals |
| Learning | Projects/Learning/ | Books, courses, research |

## Routing Rules

- Keywords "code, git, bug, deploy, api, plugin, terminal, claude" → Projects/Development/
- Keywords "client, meeting, standup, sprint, project, jira, ticket" → Projects/Work/
- Keywords "personal, journal, health, goals, finance" → Projects/Personal/
- Keywords "book, course, paper, research, study, learn" → Projects/Learning/
- Keywords "daily, journal, today" → Daily/
- Ambiguous → Inbox/ (with #needs-filing tag)
